subject: Golf
Suits and Litigation
Transgender and Transsexual
lead_paragraph: Lana Lawless, the transgender woman who sued the L.P.G.A. and the Long Drivers of America last October challenging their rule that competitors be “female at birth,” has settled her case, her lawyer said.
